text: Wilhelmina International Inc. (NASDAQ: WHLM), formerly Wilhelmina Models, is a modeling and talent agency in New York City, United States. The company also has offices in Los Angeles, Miami and London. It was founded in 1967 by Wilhelmina Cooper. They give representation and management to models, entertainers, artists, musicians, and athletes. In 2009, the company became the first and only publicly traded modeling and talent agency.Multiple sources: * * * * ==References== Category:Companies based in New York City Category:Modeling agencies
